@DATABASE "N.O.M.A.D."
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - N - N.O.M.A.D."
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - N
                   ====================================

                                N.O.M.A.D.
                                ==========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(40785,255)"}          40785,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(40703,0)"}          40703,0

                         (This is my fix of the POKE supplied in ZXAMPoke)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         Rastan.
@endnode
